title: Live from Trans Musicales: Yalla Miku
Yalla Miku - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Yalla Miku performing live at the Conservatoire de Rennes 
Auditorium in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2023. Recorded December 6, 2023. 

Songs:
Premier du matin
Asmazate
Suiise
Total Karma

Simone Aubert - Synth, Keyboards, Vocals
Anouar Baouna - Guembri, Loutar, Karkabou, Vocals, Flutes
Vincent Bertholet - Bass, Vocals
Cyril Bondi - Drums, Vocals
Samuel Ades - Krar, Vocals
Ali Boushaki - Darbouka, Bendir, Vocals
Cyril Yeterian - Bang, Guitar, Vocals

Audio Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Guest Audio Engineer: David Chesnel
Audio Mixer: Julian Martlew
Mastering: Julian Martlew
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Scott Holpainen
